# ACKO Elevated Theme

Activated via `<html data-theme="elevated">`. A light-background, high-contrast, premium visual treatment. The page background stays light — only component chrome changes.

## Design Principles

- **Glass morphism**: translucent backgrounds with `backdrop-filter: blur(14px)`
- **Gradient CTAs**: convex gradient buttons with layered inner/outer shadows
- **Elevated shadows**: slightly deeper and more colorful than the standard light theme
- **Border gradients**: 135° purple gradient borders on outline-style elements
- **Convex overlays**: subtle `::before` pseudo-element gradients for 3D depth

## Activation

```html
<html data-theme="elevated">
```

Scoped in CSS via `[data-theme="elevated"]`.

## Semantic Token Overrides

The elevated theme inherits most tokens from the light theme but overrides:

### Surfaces
| Token | Elevated Value |
|-------|---------------|
| `--color-surface` | `grey-white` |
| `--color-surface-overlay` | `color-mix(in srgb, grey-800 8%, transparent)` |

### Shadows (deeper, slate-tinted)
| Token | Elevated Value |
|-------|---------------|
| `--shadow-sm` | `0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,0.06)` |
| `--shadow-md` | `0 4px 18px rgba(15,23,42,0.08)` |
| `--shadow-lg` | `0 10px 32px rgba(15,23,42,0.12)` |
| `--shadow-xl` | `0 18px 55px rgba(15,23,42,0.14)` |

## Elevated-Specific Tokens

These tokens only exist in the elevated theme and are used by component CSS for premium treatments:

### Glass Backgrounds
| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--elevated-glass-bg` | `color-mix(in srgb, grey-white 86%, transparent)` |
| `--elevated-glass-bg-hover` | `color-mix(in srgb, grey-white 94%, transparent)` |
| `--elevated-glass-bg-active` | `color-mix(in srgb, grey-white 98%, transparent)` |

### Glass Borders
| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--elevated-glass-border` | `color-mix(in srgb, purple-500 22%, transparent)` |
| `--elevated-glass-border-strong` | `color-mix(in srgb, purple-600 34%, transparent)` |

### Glow & Border Gradient
| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--elevated-glow` | `0 0 0 1px var(--elevated-glass-border)` |
| `--elevated-glow-hover` | `0 0 0 1px var(--elevated-glass-border-strong), var(--shadow-lg)` |
| `--elevated-border-gradient` | `linear-gradient(135deg, purple-600, purple-400)` |

### Primary CTA (Convex Gradient)
| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--elevated-primary-gradient` | `linear-gradient(180deg, purple-400 0%, purple-500 20%, purple-600 100%)` |
| `--elevated-primary-gradient-hover` | `linear-gradient(180deg, purple-400 0%, purple-500 10%, purple-700 100%)` |
| `--elevated-primary-shadow` | Inner highlight + inner bottom + outer glow + ambient |
| `--elevated-primary-shadow-hover` | Intensified version of primary shadow |

### Convex Overlay
| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--elevated-convex-overlay` | `linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 22%, transparent 32%, rgba(0,0,0,0.02) 100%)` |

### Danger CTA (Cerise Gradient)
| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--elevated-danger-gradient` | `linear-gradient(180deg, cerise-400 0%, cerise-500 20%, cerise-600 100%)` |
| `--elevated-danger-gradient-hover` | `linear-gradient(180deg, cerise-400 0%, cerise-500 10%, cerise-700 100%)` |
| `--elevated-danger-shadow` | Inner highlight + inner bottom + outer glow + ambient |
| `--elevated-danger-shadow-hover` | Intensified version of danger shadow |

### Success CTA (Green Gradient)
| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| `--elevated-success-gradient` | `linear-gradient(180deg, green-400 0%, green-500 20%, green-600 100%)` |
| `--elevated-success-gradient-hover` | `linear-gradient(180deg, green-400 0%, green-500 10%, green-700 100%)` |
| `--elevated-success-shadow` | Inner highlight + inner bottom + outer glow + ambient |
| `--elevated-success-shadow-hover` | Intensified version of success shadow |

